<p class="content-box-h-1">DESCRIPTION</p>
<p class="basic-text">The textile science option emphasizes textiles and biofibers, textile production, and issues concerning the global textile industry. Professional support in related sciences and business is required. The program is planned for students interested in sales, research, or management in the textile industry. It is also recommended for students who plan to go on to graduate school in either textiles or related sciences. <span class="basic-text-bold">Students are eligible to receive a minor in chemistry from the UNL College of Arts and Sciences.</span></p>
